data.title: Oando Annual Report 2014
data.meta_description: Oando Annual Report 2014 - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text: Oando PLC is an integrated energy solutions group based in sub-Saharan Africa with operations across multiple sectors of the oil and gas industry. The document provides an overview of Oando's strategic business divisions, including exploration and production, energy services, gas and power, marketing, supply and trading, and terminaling. It also outlines Oando's mission, vision, global footprint, and corporate culture centered around values like teamwork, respect, integrity, passion and professionalism.
